    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093050/extras/8b6f429f5722b694c50c83fab6892d80.poster.avif?t=1760986413\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093050/extras/8b6f429f5722b694c50c83fab6892d80.webm?t=1760986413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093050/extras/8b6f429f5722b694c50c83fab6892d80.mp4?t=1760986413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><strong>跟随节奏自动攻击：</strong> <br>你的乐器将随音乐节拍自动攻击。跟随节拍点击，大幅增强伤害！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093050/extras/6df4b1127ef5289c310a5e747f414d2f.poster.avif?t=1760986413\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093050/extras/6df4b1127ef5289c310a5e747f414d2f.webm?t=1760986413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093050/extras/6df4b1127ef5289c310a5e747f414d2f.mp4?t=1760986413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><strong>加強独奏：</strong> <br>击败敌人并储存能量，积攒独奏值！发动独奏技能，触发炫目动画和群攻效果，将敌人一扫而空。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093050/extras/81fda3ce64077f642ecb303fa8c16009.poster.avif?t=1760986413\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093050/extras/81fda3ce64077f642ecb303fa8c16009.webm?t=1760986413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093050/extras/81fda3ce64077f642ecb303fa8c16009.mp4?t=1760986413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><strong>强化升级：</strong> <br>每轮战斗后，你可以选择强化升级选项，学习各类乐器的创意“合奏”，愈战愈强。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093050/extras/825110348d656f1a1dad4399184f41b1.poster.avif?t=1760986413\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093050/extras/825110348d656f1a1dad4399184f41b1.webm?t=1760986413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093050/extras/825110348d656f1a1dad4399184f41b1.mp4?t=1760986413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><strong>附身机制：</strong> <br>罗克西的乐队被困在无尽循环中，永无止境地为死神演奏。通过召唤乐队成员的灵魂附身，罗克西将获得力量进行反击，帮助他们重获自由！",
